Functionality:
OpenFlow 1.3 Plugin will support the following functionality
     
* Session Management 
* Connection State Management.
* Mapping function(Infrastructure to OF structures).
* Connection establishment will be handled by opensource netty.io library.

Activities in OF plugin module:
1. Existing ODL OpenFlow 1.0 plugin will be updated to support OpenFlow 1.3.
2. Integration with OpenFlow 1.3 library.
3. Integration with corresponding SAL infrastructure.
4. OF 1.3 plugin and OF 1.0 will be integrated as single bundle.

